[[=]]
**SCP-6046** - //Marble Madness//

Written by [[*user MirageTD]]
**[[span style="font-size: 80%;"]][[[miragetd | MORE BY THIS AUTHOR]]][[/span]]**
[[include :scp-wiki:component:ratio-bar pie=--]]
[[/=]]
